  "body": "```javascript\r\n        <scroller append=\"tree\">\r\n            <refresh class=\"refresh-view\" display=\"{{refresh_display}}\" onrefresh=\"onrefresh\">\r\n                <loading-indicator class=\"indicator\"></loading-indicator>\r\n            </refresh>\r\n            <header>\r\n                <input type=\"text\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"查询\" />\r\n            </header>\r\n            <div repeat=\"{{data}}\" track-by=\"{{name_pinyin_first}}\" id=\"letter-{{name_pinyin_first.toUpperCase()}}\">\r\n                <div class=\"header\">\r\n                    <text class=\"header-title\">{{name_pinyin_first.toUpperCase()}}</text>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"item\" repeat=\"{{data}}\" track-by=\"{{id}}\">\r\n                    <text class=\"item-title\">{{name}}</text>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </scroller>\r\n```\r\n![图片](http://www.xwxq.gov.cn/upload/2016/1230/1483065907323.jpg)\r\n去掉scroller的append属性，就能在顶部显示了",
